snippet.title: Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2009 (PS2) - Intro
snippet.description: The opening movie for Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 2009, a baseball video game by Konami. Reuploaded in higher quality than previously available (and I also somewhat recently uploaded the Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu NEXT intro, which is nearly identical, so sorry if it feels like you've seen this one recently).
